text: Arne Knudsen (24 May 1923 - 19 February 2010) was a Norwegian gymnast. He represented the club Drammens TF and competed at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1923 births Category:2010 deaths Category:People from Drammen Category:Norwegian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Norway Category:gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics
